strong></p><p>Build trust in machine assisted models by using expert data scientist to run them alongside existing models. In such a rapidly growing technological advanced environment, speculation and doubt can often be triggered, due to it’s unfamiliarity and complexity. Bringing AI into industries that are not as familiar to it, or are heavily comprised with Generations Xers and Baby Boomers can be difficult, hence running them in parallel to existing models can validate their accuracy, while fostering collaboration between expert data scientists and citizen data scientists. </p><div><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/9Ikp4vk92fcMsW2KWEzwLlsesVfpr5dPwbv17nW3-hyXxvLVCkhvWLMuoMzLKhJcHMEg1lDZH-BtQcuCmc1BgwCr8Ek6w4OkaiYt9HEGE_Qv2UwW6w6Du_ZMqIfCUivpvWLuZRkg\" alt=\"\" /></div><p>   3. <strong>Monitor</strong></p><p>In order to measure and monitor the success the software brings to you, monitor results and other elements. This can include observing augmented analytics capabilities and roadmaps of established BI and analytics. Furthermore, you are advised to monitor data science and machine-learning platform vendors, startups and open-source products. Focus on the requirements for upfront setup and data preparation, on the types of data that can be analyzed, and on the types and range of algorithms supported. Finally, monitor the accuracy of findings. This, just like the two previous steps will help your company be aware of the features the software provides, and help build trust within your enterprise. </p><div><img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/jqCMZq_tPdu0V1O6LtK_w6Sj13P4YvIddzcbJ7figXaDJiwA1azj7EQPdeELIRgCSvgIz_jQErwGx6gHl_GMkTyHiRUNDYbIK8-epZ4tnYvTpOOjhYF1Hd_ImPjG2fzL1qiD_Iug\" alt=\"\" /></div><p>If Augmented Analytics is the future of Data and Analytics, take your company to the future too. Use next generation analytics to modernise your enterprise, drive results, generate efficiencies and build satisfaction. For a further analysis on Augmented Analytics along with its key findings and strategic planning assumptions, download the Gartner Report Below.</p>','3 steps to adopt the Future of Data and Analytics','','draft','closed','open','','','','','1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://zensciences.com/kpisoft/?p=698',0,'post','',0),(699,1,'1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Your Blog Post Title Here...','','draft','closed','open','','','','','1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://zensciences.com/kpisoft/?p=699',0,'post','',0),(700,1,'1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p>Test</p>','Test','','draft','closed','open','','','','','1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://zensciences.com/kpisoft/?p=700',0,'post','',0),(701,1,'1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p>adad</p>','ada','','draft','closed','open','','','','','1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://zensciences.com/kpisoft/?p=701',0,'post','',0),(702,1,'1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p>This is my test blog post</p>','Blog Test Post','','draft','closed','open','','','','','1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://zensciences.com/kpisoft/?p=702',0,'post','',0),(703,1,'1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','This is a test blog','','draft','closed','open','','','','','1970-01-01 00:00:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://zensciences.com/kpisoft/?p=703',0,'post','',0),(779,1,'2020-07-02 07:24:59','2020-07-02 07:24:59','','AI-artwork','','inherit','closed','closed','','ai-artwork-2','','','2020-07-02 07:24:59','2020-07-02 07:24:59','',560,'https://webuat.kpisoft.com/new_kpisoft/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/AI20artwork-1-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(783,1,'2020-07-02 07:25:02','2020-07-02 07:25:02','','augmented-analytics','','inherit','closed','closed','','augmented-analytics','','','2020-07-02 07:25:02','2020-07-02 07:25:02','',562,'https://webuat.kpisoft.com/new_kpisoft/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Imagea201-1-1-1.jpg'